[quest]Dyson Sphere Module Launch Site[/quest]

§6Machine Type: §aDyson Sphere Program: Launch Site§r

Launch Dyson Sphere Components into orbit to form a Dyson Sphere | Accepted Components: Launch Vehicles & Solar Sails

§1§9NO§r Overclock
§1§9NO§r Extra Parallel

Higher Tier of Elevator Motor Module = Faster Launching

Inputting §9Space Warper§r will enable overload mode; Reduces Launch Intervals. 

Will join the Wireless EU Network if no Energy Hatch is installed.

§6 --- Details --- §r

Final progress time = recipe time / (module tier * overload mode parameter)
Overload Parameter = t ^ [§c1§r / (§c1000§r*§c900§r/t + §c5§r)] | t = Overload Time
Every Space Warper provides §c15§r minutes of overload mode.
All Space Warper inputted will be consumed immediately

§6 --- Dyson Sphere Program --- §r

Launching Solar Sails increases §aSolar Sail§r amount in the Dyson Sphere. 
Launching Small Launch Vehicle increases §aNode§r amount in the Dyson Sphere. 

Dyson Sphere Energy Credit = Solar Sail Output (default §c524,288§r) * Solar Sail Amount * (Node + §c1§r)^§c0.8§r
Every Node by default can absorb §c256§r Solar Sails.

If unabsorbed solar sails amount is > §c2048§r, the excess may be destroyed.

Every §a30§r minutes has §c1§r/§c5000§r chance to decrease Solar Sail amount.
While decreasing, every Dyson Sphere has §c1§r/§c4§r chance to destroy Solar Sails | The amount destroyed is §c1§r/§c2§r of the excess.

[note]Best Planet to put the Dyson Sphere Program is §9Vega§r[/note]
